title: Old Video of Russian Rocket Crash Claimed as Indian Missile Test
subtitle: Viral Video of Indian Missile Test Failed Fact Check: We found that not only is the video old, it is not even related to India. It dates back to 2013 and shows the explosion of Russian Proton-M rocket.
author: www.thequint.com
vclaim:
A video showing a rocket ramming into the ground is being circulated to claim that the test of an Indian missile has failed.

However, we found that not only is the video old, it is not even related to India. It dates back to 2013 and shows the explosion of Russian Proton-M rocket.
